{"tid":1189514,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"仆街喇，呢隻昆蟲咩黎幫幫手","createTime":"2019-06-06T22:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:44:11.000Z","uid":107327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e164824f12b9f5b0f0fd148adbce5d829dcb9ee","tid":1189514,"uid":107327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T22:51:12.000Z","msg":"仆街，岩岩去個廁所呢隻係腳度，唔識飛好似淨係識跳，最尾係自己件杉度捉到，用紙巾收佢皮，一禁爆好鬼多血，但一直禁唔死，唔知係咪太細粒，<br />\n諗諗下呢幾日隻腳好似係咁比蚊咬，但唔見有蚊飛過，係咪比呢隻咬？係咪跳蚤黎？屌今次仆街喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmyH8YU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmyH8YU.png&h=526dd8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mv3MRcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMv3MRcf.png&h=74916a01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ccaa9982373a86982bc49559dab264008aa823b","tid":1189514,"uid":107327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2064ae5304f2774f16561b5f8f8f4d560aecdf72","tid":1189514,"uid":107327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63131a6f9ef4a7fb6fe0f4be6b8b0ccc8927768","tid":1189514,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:53:29.000Z","msg":"搬屋"},{"pid":"9efb158aa83c052e6d9696abe2cc2e00f1e2e8af","tid":1189514,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T00:06:14.000Z","msg":"去買農藥"},{"pid":"acd7b8aa7d1f896163e3a19df652297e7d3934e2","tid":11895